<translation id="3592624492063123732">Ungashintsha ukuze ubone amaphasiwedi kusuka kwenye iphrofayela ye-Ecosia</translation>
<translation id="8067423333018528301">I-EcosiaOS ayikwazanga ukuvumelanisa idatha yakho ngenxa yephutha lokungena ngemvume.</translation>
<translation id="2926455547526018397">I-beta ye-Ecosia</translation>
<translation id="2995860351618948435">Le khompyutha isivele inenguqulo yakamuva ye-Ecosia. Uma isofthiwe ingasebenzi, sicela ukhiphe i-Ecosia uphinde uzame futhi.</translation>
<translation id="824192326282906244">Ungashintsha umqondo wakho noma kunini kumasethingi we-Ecosia. Izivivinyo zisebenza eduze kwendlela yamanje yokulethwa kwezikhangiso, ngakho ngeke ubone izinguquko ngokushesha.</translation>
<translation id="3621704124701415791">I-Ecosia ine-Ecosia Translate eyakhelwe ngaphakathi ngakho-ke ungahumusha uma kumele wenze kanjalo</translation>
<translation id="5043324171996581320">{COUNT,plural, =0{I-Ecosia iqedile ukuvuselela. Ungasebenzisa uhlobo lwakamuva ngokushesha nje lapho uqalisa kabusha. Ngemuva kwalokho, amathebhu akho amanje azovulwa kabusha.}=1{I-Ecosia iqedile ukuvuselela. Ungasebenzisa uhlobo lwakamuva ngokushesha nje lapho uqalisa kabusha. Ngemuva kwalokho, amathebhu akho amanje azovulwa kabusha. Iwindi lakho le-Incognito ngeke liphinde livuleke.}one{I-Ecosia iqedile ukuvuselela. Ungasebenzisa uhlobo lwakamuva ngokushesha nje lapho uqalisa kabusha. Ngemuva kwalokho, amathebhu akho amanje azovulwa kabusha. Amawindi akho angu-# e-Incognito ngeke aze aphinde avuleke.}other{I-Ecosia iqedile ukuvuselela. Ungasebenzisa uhlobo lwakamuva ngokushesha nje lapho uqalisa kabusha. Ngemuva kwalokho, amathebhu akho amanje azovulwa kabusha. Amawindi akho angu-# e-Incognito ngeke aze aphinde avuleke.}}</translation>
