<translation id="8696852719113991652">Ukuze ususe i-Ecosia Account yakho ku-Ecosia, phuma ngemvume ku-Ecosia ekhasini Lamasethingi</translation>
<translation id="5405885279794834338">Phatha amakhukhi ezinkampani zangaphandle kanye nokuvikela ukulandelela (<ph name="URL"/>)</translation>
